        <title type="html"><![CDATA[[翻译]SKI文明的衰落]]></title>
        <id>https://Xiqiu-li.github.io/post/fan-yi-ski-wen-ming-de-shuai-luo/</id>
        <link href="https://Xiqiu-li.github.io/post/fan-yi-ski-wen-ming-de-shuai-luo/">
        </link>
        <updated>2021-02-12T10:13:39.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://bartoszmilewski.com/2020/09/06/the-fall-of-the-ski-civilization/">原文</a></p>
<h2 id="code摘要最新的对闪灵文明的语言和文学的破译为我们在闪灵文明的历史-科学和哲学方面提供了重大帮助-code"><code><br>
摘要:<br>
最新的对闪灵文明的语言和文学的破译，为我们在闪灵文明的历史、科学和哲学方面提供了重大帮助。<br>
</code></h2>
<p>在莱姆达组合星（也称闪烁之星）的第三颗行星上发现的最古老的文本谈到了闪烁之星的史前思想。远古的应用之书(Application)假定存在之本质是分解，象征性的表示为</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A = BC</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>这意味着<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span>可以被分解成<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span>和<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>，其突破性在于，如果<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>本身也可以被分解</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>G</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C = FG</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mord mathdefault">G</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>那么<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span>可以被进一步分解成</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>G</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A = B(FG)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mord mathdefault">G</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>相似的，如果<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span>可以被分解成</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B = DE</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>然后</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mo>)</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A = (DE)C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>在后一种情况下（而不是前一种），习惯性去掉括号，简化为</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A = DEC</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>在这些发现之后，闪灵文明经历了一个被称为「伟大分解」的时代，这个时代持续了近三千年，在此期间，任何可以分解的东西都被成功地分解了。<br>
在「伟大分解」的末年，一个新的学派出现了，他们宣称，如果事物可以被分解成部件，那么他们也可以由这些部件重组。</p>
<p>最初，这种想法遭到了强烈的反对。反对意见认为，分解之后重组不会改变任何东西。这个问题通过引入一个被称作「眼」的特殊对象而得以解决，这个特殊对象被标识为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span></span></span></span>，通过其仅留下原物的独特性质来定义</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I A = A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>在引入<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span></span></span></span>之后，一个缺乏变化的漫长停滞时代随之而来</p>
<p>我们也没有太多下一时代的记录，因为它被记载为致力于遗忘和促进无知。它开始于引进<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>K</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">K</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span></span></span></span>，会忽略他的一个输入的东西。</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>K</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">K AB = A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>需要注意的是，这个定义是带括号版本的简写</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>K</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>)</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(K A)B = A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>提出<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>K</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">K</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span></span></span></span>这一思想的论据是，无知是理解的重要组成部分。通过拒绝<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span>，说明了<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span>很重要。我们抽象掉了非必要的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>举一个例子，如果我们分解<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C =AB</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>刚好由一个拥有相似的分解的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D = AE</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>然后<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>K</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">K</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span></span></span></span>会从<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>和<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span></span></span></span>中抽象出<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span>的部分。从<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>K</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">K</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span></span></span></span>的角度看，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>和<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span></span></span></span>之间没有区别。</p>
<p>在这个无知时代，唯一的积极成果就是抽象数学的发展，闪灵思想家们认为，如果你忽略了所讨论的水果的特殊性，那么三个苹果和三个橘子就没有区别了。数字三就这样诞生了，接着是许多其他的例子（四和七，仅举几个例子）。</p>
<p>在闪灵文明的最后的工业阶段，导致他们毁灭的是引入<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>。闪灵的工业是以批量生产为基础，大规模生产是以复制和重用为基础。假设你有一个可重复使用的部件<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>允许你复制<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>并让它和<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span>，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span>结合</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S ABC = (AC)(BC)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>如果你把<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span>和<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span>视为抽象的部分——这就是忽略整体某些部分的结果——<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span></span></span></span>让你用<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>代替那些被遗忘的部分。</p>
<p>或者反过来</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>S</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E = S ABC</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>它告诉你一个对象可以被分解成两个拥有共同点的部分，这个共同点是<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>不幸的是，在工业化时期，许多闪灵人失去了他们的身份，他们发现</p>
<p>$I = S K K $</p>
<p>的确如此</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>I</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>S</mi><mi>K</mi><mi>K</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>K</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>K</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I A = S K K A = K A(K A) = A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>但最终，促使他们走向死亡的是存在的危机。他们失去了活下去的意志，因为他们不知道<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">Y</span></span></span></span></p>
<h3 id="后记">后记</h3>
<p>在将这篇论文提交给《组合》杂志后，审稿人告知我们，俄罗斯逻辑学家Moses Schönfinkel在地球独立开创了SKI组合子理论。根据这位审稿人的说法，生命的意义的答案就是<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">Y</span></span></span></span>组合子，它引入了递归，可以表示为</p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>Y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>S</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>K</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>S</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>I</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>S</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>S</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>K</mi><mi>S</mi><mo>)</mo><mi>K</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>K</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>S</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>I</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Y = S(K(S I I))(S(S(K S)K)(K(S I I)))</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">Y</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></p>
<p>我们无法证实这一断言，因为它把我们带入了一个兔子洞。</p>
]]></content>
